d-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#advantages-of-traditional-banking\" title=\"Advantages of Traditional Banking\">Advantages of Traditional Banking<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#they-offer-several-banking-options\" title=\"They Offer Several Banking Options\">They Offer Several Banking Options<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#they-have-a-high-level-of-convenience\" title=\"They Have a High Level of Convenience\">They Have a High Level of Convenience<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#they-offer-both-digital-and-traditional-services\" title=\"They Offer Both Digital and Traditional Services\">They Offer Both Digital and Traditional Services<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#they-accept-cash-deposits\" title=\"They Accept Cash Deposits\">They Accept Cash Deposits<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#services-offered-by-traditional-banks-are-secure\" title=\"Services Offered by Traditional Banks are Secure\">Services Offered by Traditional Banks are Secure<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#what-are-the-disadvantages-of-traditional-banking\" title=\"What are the Disadvantages of Traditional Banking?\">What are the Disadvantages of Traditional Banking?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#traditional-banks-have-a-wide-range-of-fees\" title=\"Traditional Banks have a Wide Range of Fees\">Traditional Banks have a Wide Range of Fees<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#poor-customer-service\" title=\"Poor Customer Service\">Poor Customer Service<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#what-are-the-alternatives-to-traditional-banking\" title=\"What are the Alternatives to Traditional Banking?\">What are the Alternatives to Traditional Banking?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#banking-using-local-or-community-banks\" title=\"Banking Using Local or Community Banks\">Banking Using Local or Community Banks<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#banking-using-credit-unions\" title=\"Banking Using Credit Unions\">Banking Using Credit Unions<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#banking-using-online-banks\" title=\"Banking using Online Banks\">Banking using Online Banks<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/pros-and-cons-of-traditional-banking-institutions\/#choosing-between-traditional-banking-vs-modern-banking\" title=\"Choosing Between Traditional Banking vs Modern Banking\">Choosing Between Traditional Banking vs Modern Banking<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-is-traditional-banking\"><\/span>What is Traditional Banking?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The banking business is one of the old-fashioned industries still operating. Therefore, <a href=\"https:\/\/businessyield.com\/accounting\/traditional-banks\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">traditional banking<\/a> comprises banks that offer physical building services and have a domestic banking license. Some of the main features of traditional banking include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>They have a physical presence<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They have their own branded debit and credit cards<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They have several members of staff<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They have dedicated account managers<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They offer face-to-face customer service<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Most banks try to meet each customer\u2019s needs despite <a href=\"https:\/\/businessyield.com\/accounting\/traditional-banks\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">several traditional banking problems<\/a> by adopting electronic banking systems while providing common banking services such as in-person assistance and loans.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/business-account-digital-banking.jpg\" alt=\"image showing the paperwork that Traditional banking system requires \" class=\"wp-image-766\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/business-account-digital-banking.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/